{"tid":893898,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打人央視女記者缺席聆訊","createTime":"2018-11-08T03:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T08:10:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"387c05b8e144e41019c539a94ebc8200065f3cfa","tid":893898,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:52:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181108/20541159\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181108%2F20541159&d=B7GBdyep%2FDRCAqI41TKoAEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=1aa2592b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181108%2F20541159&h=09962432\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20181108/20541159</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年11月08日 <br />\n<br />\n打人央視女記者缺席聆訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181108/large/08la5p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181108%2Flarge%2F08la5p4.jpg&h=69c9406f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n央視女記者孔琳琳9月底在英國保守黨年會上大吵大鬧。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】早前在英國保守黨年會上掌摑香港義工的中央電視台記者孔琳琳，被英國當局控告普通襲擊後昨日提堂，但孔琳琳未有出席聆訊。控辯雙方均指，在英國時間昨日早上才收到一條新的閉路電視片段，因此申請押後並獲法官同意；案件將於本月21日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n伯明翰警方在上月25日證實孔琳琳被正式起訴普通襲擊，案件昨日在伯明翰裁判法院提堂，但被告孔琳琳未有現身。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n押至21日再審<br />\n<br />\n控辯雙方均在庭上指出，由於在昨晨11時才收到一條新的閉路電視片段，需要更多時間研究，因此申請押後。法官同意押後申請，但特別提醒辯方律師須與孔琳琳溝通，下次開庭她應該出席聆訊。法官最終決定將案件延至11月21日再審。<br />\n<br />\n案件發生於9月30日，英國保守黨在伯明翰舉辦以「香港自由、法治和自治的侵蝕」為題的座談會，由保守黨人權委員會主席布魯斯（Fiona Bruce）主持，並邀請了民主黨創黨主席李柱銘、戴耀廷、羅冠聰及香港監察主席羅傑斯（Benedict Rogers）任嘉賓。<br />\n<br />\n座談會近尾聲時，孔琳琳突然大吵大鬧，大罵在場嘉賓「分裂中國」、「漢奸」及「反中」，一名香港留學生義工工作人員請她離場時，她更掌摑對方，最終被伯明翰警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n■特約記者何敬淘  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n無屍無目擊者　肢解前妻阿姨切肉員謀殺罪成<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n警涉假牌霸車位　稱不知司機身份"},{"pid":"a1cb423997456576a21df810121dd144f09af60e","tid":893898,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"通緝啦"},{"pid":"e1995e690ae98f29037a6ddf3ba30086a7168665","tid":893898,"uid":73586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"返撚左大陸啦"},{"pid":"ba983af435dae6dc91714feab480e7e0030f85d1","tid":893898,"uid":4431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:56:22.000Z","msg":"係咪成個歐洲都唔去得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b0e08e008827cc478ef5d6644093d6acd2f170","tid":893898,"uid":174766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:58:07.000Z","msg":"支那畜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6264d36750978c2c1b4715440b0581f1f804f9","tid":893898,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e1995e690ae98f29037a6ddf3ba30086a7168665","tid":893898,"uid":73586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"返撚左大陸啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"我寧願喺英國坐監都唔想去支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e171cceca156b5908394fc344fd0d287e7ec83","tid":893898,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T07:47:08.000Z","msg":"條八婆玩膠搏長期居留,快啲拉去坐返十年八年"},{"pid":"9d2656b49093c3fafb4769c58e6cafd7b7a0fe5e","tid":893898,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T08:05:49.000Z","msg":"潛逃左啦"},{"pid":"e250f9e087de6d0ea5772a455445fdf4696e4384","tid":893898,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d2656b49093c3fafb4769c58e6cafd7b7a0fe5e","tid":893898,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T08:05:49.000Z","msg":"潛逃左啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"咁咪永遠唔駛返去？咁大犧牲？<i